> From: Martin Andersson <t3tr1s@yahoo.com>
> theres a bug in sample_editor_zoom_[in|out]_clicked in
> soundtracker-0.6.7-pre3. you can only zoom in to
> minimal of 2 samples. With zoom to selection you can
> zoom in to 1 sample, but then you cant zoom out again
> :-) A quick source fix was to double the values of the
> variables ns,ne,l and divide ns and ne by 2 in the
> call to sample_display_set_window.

